毛吖嘛，好巴閉呀？<br />\n你知唔知條三文魚游走咗佢食唔到；<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢條女比老虎，屌，佢救唔到。<br />\n你知唔知Grizzly諗緊咩呀？<br />\n話畀你聽佢唔想做Grizzly，<br />\n佢唔想做🐻🐻，<br />\n但係佢冇辦法，冇得返轉頭。<br />\n係呀，每個人都有偶像，我都有。<br />\n其實，食唔食到魚同蜂蜜，我理唔到咁多，<br />\n但係我想話畀你聽，做左🐻🐻，就冇得返轉頭。"},{"pid":"f2fb15e140055e4337997432d934b95ac14fde5a","tid":2072593,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87cb7bbb7f382dbf8f9a3b50ef8618060ba78387","tid":2072593,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"鍾意鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:53:11.000Z","msg":"咦～死基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f220f2ff0fde8b51f1ddb4dba1bc4fb8e21c0eeb","tid":2072593,"uid":10214,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwEu4Oc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwEu4Oc.jpg&h=28731c69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efdd0734f9d4d508c02d2126afaf9c62d9c95668","tid":2072593,"uid":105396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"咁請問到底係熊啤啤定係啤啤熊"},{"pid":"cc81805e952c1f40112ae3b5339cb7d77db01798","tid":2072593,"uid":359711,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"efdd0734f9d4d508c02d2126afaf9c62d9c95668","tid":2072593,"uid":105396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"咁請問到底係熊啤啤定係啤啤熊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"熊啤啤係講隻熊係度叫<br />\n啤啤熊係講隻熊識叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔識</span>"},{"pid":"0594d13019983dcaf0e9953973accb9c5fa27f66","tid":2072593,"uid":299433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"熊軍世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49162dc748f38fb9c3e894d4b0977b7a18f3a976","tid":2072593,"uid":43381,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:02:17.000Z","msg":